org.onyxplatform.api.java

Class Lifecycles

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.onyxplatform.api.java.OnyxVector
      • org.onyxplatform.api.java.Lifecycles

  • public class Lifecycles
extends OnyxVector
    Lifecycles objects are a set of Lifecycle objects that can be applied to Tasks running as part of a job. Lifecycles derive from OnyxVector.
